WEBVTT

00:00:01.040 --> 00:00:04.791
I'm here to offer you
a new way to think about my field,

00:00:04.815 --> 00:00:06.583
artificial intelligence.

00:00:06.607 --> 00:00:08.621
I think the purpose of AI

00:00:08.645 --> 00:00:12.079
is to empower humans
with machine intelligence.

00:00:13.286 --> 00:00:15.736
And as machines get smarter,

00:00:15.760 --> 00:00:17.013
we get smarter.

00:00:17.907 --> 00:00:20.419
I call this "humanistic AI" --

00:00:20.443 --> 00:00:24.114
artificial intelligence
designed to meet human needs

00:00:24.138 --> 00:00:27.069
by collaborating and augmenting people.

